法規內容.條文內容:
The importers or their agents shall submit to the plant quarantine authority a completed application form along with supporting documents listed as follows before the regulated articles from other countries are entered into and stored within the free trade zones:
1.Phytosanitary certificate issued by the exporting country; but exemptions published by the plant quarantine authority are not required;
2.Delivery order;
3.Import declaration form; and
4.Affidavit and a post-entry use plan or other proofing documentation.
